ws and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience our history  life sciences skip to main content  saintgobain main site   years site search google appliance enter the terms you wish to search for en fr de contact us  search this site our history for more than  years saintgobain performance plastics and our family of companies have collectively supplied the world with highperformance polymer products for the most demanding applications as part of compagnie de saintgobain one of the worlds top  industrial corporations saintgobain performance plastics is dedicated to leading the way through innovation operating from a global network of facilities we focus heavily on research and development pioneering unique material compounds and processing techniques and creating strong working partnerships with our customers to develop highperformance products for medical oems  throughout our long history of pioneering products – including tygon® and biosil® tubing – saintgobain performance plastics has partnered with medical oems to meet the constant challenges of a hugely diverse market we take pride in providing molded and extruded products for the most demanding applications saintgobain has expertise in silicone molding and extrusion as well as extensive experience in extruding materials ranging from thermoplastics and fluoropolymers to custom formulations we also provide confidential contract fabrication of silicone thermoplastic or fluoropolymer medical component assemblies  from our worldwide network of facilities saintgobain is strategically positioned to partner with companies across the globe to provide you with the highest quality products and the most valuable manufacturing processes we employ world class manufacturing techniques to ensure your component is right the first time while keeping costs under control our engineers stand ready to partner with you throughout the entire life cycle of your product — from design and development to prototype and tool build into full production our mission to be the most soughtafter component supplier in the medical device industry by supplying superior service and technology utilizing highperformance materials our vision to add unparalleled value beyond price to our customers by knowing your business and anticipating your needs in order to consistently provide innovative solutions that exceed your expectations contact us  saintgobain performance plastics all rights reserved about a world leader with unparalleled material expertise in silicone thermoplastic elastomers and fluoropolymers saintgobain is the processing expert in molding extrusion and allencompassing custom fabrication for medical oems leading the way through our global resources and technological expertise we are committed to providing you with outstanding quality and exceptional value by developing innovative highperformance solutions for your medical device needs about us our history contact us locations sustainabilitycorporate initiatives regulatory compliance privacy terms of use integrated solutions as the leader in material and process development saintgobain partners with you to develop integrated solutions to meet your evolving needs for innovative medical device designs   rapid prototyping tooling custom compounding material and product development advanced technologies saintgobain pairs our materials expertise with stateoftheart processing technology to develop innovative solutions that deliver consistent and reliable performance   medical extrusionsilicone fluoropolymers thermoplastics compass technology medical moldinglsrhcr molding silicone micromolding insertovermolding twoshot silicone thermoplastic molding compressiontransfer molding material expertise backed by a rich history of expertise with advanced materials saintgobain brings an unparalleled knowledge of highperformance polymers to the medical market   custom silicone formulations thermoplastic products other materials fluorop